        </uncertainty>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated value based on literature value (see comments of the other parametres present in this dataset) and expert opinion. In the case when no industry/literature data are available about the type of cooling or directly fraction, cooling water, to air specific for the process a default assumption is applied. It is assumed that the once-through cooling system is used in 50% of all cases and recirculating system is used in another 50% of all cases.</comment>
      </parameter>
